offset_bottom = -27.0
text = "- the teeth_spiral is in teeth_spiral_ANIMATED in lvl2 because it is the only way to make it spin around its own axis.
- does not work as is (crazy glitch)
- when turned into area 2D it only spins one cycle then glitches in the same way, also no collision obvs
- when animated body and area2D are layered, the two issues are combined (area2D's collision shape is animated for one spin cycle, animatable body is stuck in a glitch)
- if you can think of something...anything... blessed be onto you and your progeny"
metadata/_edit_use_anchors_ = true

